🔟 WORKING PROCESS
Step 1:
Citizen clicks SOS → GPS auto-captured.

Step 2:
Backend creates incident record.

Step 3:
Nearest police and ambulance calculated using Haversine formula.

Step 4:
Real-time WebSocket notification sent.

Step 5:
Hospital alerted when ambulance transports patient.

Step 6:
Incident closed after confirmation.

1️⃣1️⃣ NEAREST RESOURCE ALGORITHM
The system uses Haversine formula to calculate distance between two GPS coordinates.

Formula:

Distance = 2R × arcsin(√a)

Where R = Earth radius (6371 km)

The system selects the minimum distance available resource.

